data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully updated townhome in Wild Wing Plantation!  This end unit home with a 2-car garage has been meticulously maintained and is ready for the next owner!  This is the perfect home for retirement living, a growing family or someone working or attending Coastal Carolina University!  This entire townhome has been updated from the original builder grade finishes with beautiful quartzite in the kitchen and a subway tile backsplash, LVP flooring throughout the living spaces, fresh paint and fully updated bathrooms.  The master suite with full bath and walk-in closet is downstairs providing easy living for the resident while two spacious guest rooms, full bath, laundry room and a loft space are upstairs.  A private patio is set up in the back for outdoor living.  This townhome has it all!  The Fairways at Wild Wing Plantation is situated in the heart of Horry county, close to Carolina Forest, Conway and a short 15 minute ride to the beach!  Do not hesitate on this one!  Call today to schedule your private showing!
